                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310106-138-defend1224 t18310106-138-punish791"></join>
               Whipped
            </rs> and Discharged.</p>
               <p>KNOTT - <rs id="t18310106-138-verdict792" type="verdictDescription">
